lass=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/PreDefinition/Main.html#Lean.Elab.checkTerminationByHints\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">checkTerminationByHints</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">preDefs</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/PreDefinition/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.PreDefinition\">PreDefinition</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Checks consistency of a clique of TerminationHints:\n\n* If not all have a hint, the hints are ignored (log error)\n* None have both `termination_by` and `partial_fixpoint` (throw error)\n* If one has `structural` or `partial_fixpoint`, check that all have it (else throw error)\n* A `structural` should not have a `decreasing_by` (else log error)\n\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/PreDefinition/Main.html#Lean.Elab.checkTerminationByHints","kind":"def","line":158,"name":"Lean.Elab.checkTerminationByHints","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/00659f8e6071d7e46131ed643bf8003b99b044e9/src/Lean/Elab/PreDefinition/Main.lean#L158-L262"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/PreDefinition/Main.html#Lean.Elab.ensureFunIndReservedNamesAvailable\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">ensureFunIndReservedNamesAvailable</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">preDefs</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/PreDefinition/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.PreDefinition\">PreDefinition</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_